description: For sale: $579,900. You will be awed! This 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom contemporary home with huge garage is in the heart of Hermantown! There is also a dining area with patio door that leads to a back deck that overlooks the private wooded backyard. Main level also has powder room and walk-in closet in mud room with built in lockers. Upper level has unique staircases which takes you to one of 2 ways.  There are 3 bedrooms in their own separate wing with a full bath, a master suite with 2 walk-in closets, laundry and gorgeous walk-in shower and spa tub and a 25'x14' bonus room. Lower level has family room with amazing cherry built-in wall-to-wall cabinets, 5th bedroom with walk-in closet, storage room, office and a ¾ bathroom w/travertine tile shower. The heated garage is 4+ car with extra space for plenty of storage. This home is conveniently located only a 1/2 mile away from the Hermantown Schools and the new Essentia Wellness Center. description: Recently sold: $225,000. Here it is! A gem of a home in town with close to an acre of incredible, luscious outdoor space all of your own! 2 plus bedroom, 2 bath home in Duluth Heights, centrally located so buzzing downtown or roaming around on top the hill is super convenient.  Modern, crisp colors throughout the home with hardwood floors and tiled flooring.  Classic white kitchen design with large pantry, subway tile backsplash, tiled floors and even space for an eat in area. Right off the kitchen wander into the calming living room with large windows and gorgeous dark stained hardwood floors.  This is definitely the place for a quiet evening cuddled up with a book!  Main floor bathroom is tastefully designed with a tiled shower, neutral colors, and contemporary elements.  As beautiful as the main floor is the lower level boasts more living space including a large family room perfect for movie nights with friends or a play room for the kiddos!  Need an office?  It's here in lower level, away from the hustle and bustle of life upstairs.  How about a craft room, brewing room, or art room? Spend hours in this well thought out area with tile floor, chalk board walls and long counter made just for tinkering on your favorite hobby.  This yard is spectacular! Perennials all around with strategically placed gardens making this backyard an oasis for play or relaxation, it even has a back patio for those who love grilling or just hanging out and enjoying a fairy tale setting right in the back yard!  On top of all this there is a newer furnace, central air, newer windows, newer vinyl siding, a shed and a 1+ stall garage!  Wow!  So much to offer here and won't last long!!

description: Recently sold: $588,000. This next to new Hermantown home has everything you will ever want and more! From the moment you step inside you will FALL IN LOVE! Main level has front entry, formal dining room, an OPEN FLOOR PLAN w/ sprawling kitchen w/ cherry cabinets, granite and walk in pantry, open dining area w/ door to maintenance free deck overlooking private backyard, and living room w/ gas fireplace.  All also with gleaming hardwood flooring. Mudroom off garage entrance w/ walk in closet and a half bath. Upper level features master suite w/ bath that has dual sinks, tiled shower and large walk in closet. 2 more addt'l  bedrooms, full bath w/ dual sinks, an office that could be used as a bedroom and even a laundry room on this level! Lower level has workout room w/ rubber flooring that could also be a bedroom,another bedroom, full bath, loads of storage and a  ginormous family room w/ walk out to brick paver patio that has an amazing outdoor living area! This you must see! It has fan and weatherproof ceiling and privacy panels. Home has central air, security  system, epoxy garage flooring, deck seating around upper deck, nice firepit area, 3 car heated garage and oh so much more!!! Home also comes with a home warranty good until 10/22.  See it today!  Association fees $220/yr.
